quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  14,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  14,1,"alif -lam-ra ,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh aik kitaab hai jis ko hum ne tumhari taraf nazil kya hai taakay tum logon ko tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein lao, un ke rab ki tofeq se, uss khuda ke rastay par jo zabardast aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood hai"
  14,2,aur zameen aur asmano ki saari mojoodaat ka maalik hai aur sakht tabah kin saza hai qubool haq se inkaar karne walon ke liye
  14,3,"jo duniya ki zindagi ko akhirat par tarjeeh dete hain, jo Allah ke rastay se logon ko rok rahay hain aur chahtay hain ke yeh rasta ( un ki khwahisaat ke mutabiq ) terah ho jaye yeh log gumraahi mein bohat daur nikal gay hain"
  14,4,"hum ne apna pegham dainay ke liye jab kabhi koi rasool bheja hai, uss ne apni qoum hi ki zabaan mein pegham diya hai taakay woh inhen achi terhan khol kar baat samjhaye phir Allah jisay chahta hai bhatka deta hai aur jisay chahta hai hadaayat bakhshta hai, woh baala dast aur hakeem hai"
  14,5,hum iss se pehlay moose ko bhi apni nishanion ke sath bhaij chuke hain usay bhi hum ne hukum diya tha ke apni qoum ko tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein laa aur inhen tareekh Ellahi ke sabaq amooz waqeat suna kar nasiyaat kar inn waqeat mein barri nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo sabr aur shukar karne wala ho
  14,6,"yaad karo jab moose ne apni qoum se kaha"" Allah ke uss ahsaan ko yaad rakho jo is ne tum par kya hai is ne tum ko firaon walon se choraya jo tum ko sakht takleifein dete thay, tumahray larkoon ko qatal kar daaltay thay aur tumhari aurton ko zindah bacha rakhtay thay is mein tumahray rab ki taraf se tumhari barri azmaish thi"
  14,7,"aur yaad rakho, tumahray rab ne khabardaar kar diya tha ke agar shukar guzaar bano ge to mein tum ko aur ziyada nwazon ga aur agar kufran Nemat karo ge to meri saza bohat sakht hai """
  14,8,"aur moose ne kaha ke"" agar tum kufar karo aur zameen ke saaray rehne walay bhi kafir ho jayen to Allah be niaz aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood hai """
  14,9,"kya tumhe unn qomon ke halaat nahi puhanche jo tum se pehlay guzar chuki hain? qoum Nooh, Aad , samood aur unn ke baad anay wali bohat si qoumain jin ka shumaar Allah hi ko maloom hai? unn ke rasool jab unn ke paas saaf saaf baatein aur khuli khuli nishanain liye hue aeye to onhon ne apne mun mein haath daba liye aur kaha ke"" jis pegham ke sath tum beje gay ho hum is ko nahi mantay aur jis cheez ki tum hamein dawat dete ho uss ki taraf se hum sakht Khuljan aamaiz shak mein parre hue hain """
  14,10,"unn ke Rasolo-n ne kaha"" kya khuda ke baray mein shak hai jo asmano aur zameen ka khaaliq hai? woh tumhe bulaa ray = ha hai taakay tumahray qasoor maaf kere aur tum ko aik muddat muqarrar taq mohlat day"" onhon ne jawab diya"" tum kuch nahi ho magar waisay hi ensaan jaisay hum hain tum hamein unn hastiyon ki bandagi se rokna chahtay ho jin ki bandagi baap dada se hoti chali aa rahi hai acha to lao koi Sarih sanad """
  14,11,"un ke Rasolo-n ne un se kaha"" waqai hum kuch nahi hain magar tum hi jaisay ensaan lekin Allah apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai nwazta hai aur yeh hamaray ikhtiyar mein nahi hai ke tumhe koi sanad laa den sanad to Allah hi ke azan se askati hai aur Allah hi par ahal imaan ko bharosa karna chahiye"
  14,12,"aur hum kyun nah Allah par bharosa karen jabkay hamari zindagi ki raahon mein is ne hamari rahnumai ki hai? jo azeeyaten tum log hamein day rahay ho unn par hum sabr karen ge aur bhrosa karne walon ka bhrosa Allah hi par hona chahiye """
  14,13,"aakhir-kaar munkareen ne apne Rasolo-n se keh diya ke"" ya to tumhe hamari millat mein wapas aana hoga warna hum tumhe apne malik se nikaal den ge"" tab unn ke rab ne unn par wahi bhaije ke"" hum inn zaalmon ko hila kaaf kar den ge"
  14,14,"aur unn ke baad tumhe zameen mein abad karen ge yeh inaam hai uss ka jo mere huzoor jawab dahi ka khauf rakhta ho aur meri waeed se darta ho """
  14,15,onhon ne faisla chaha tha ( to yun unn ka faisla howa ) aur har Jabbar dushman haq ne mun ki khayi
  14,16,phir is ke baad agay is ke liye jahannum hai wahan ussay kutch lahoo ka sa pani peenay ko diya jaye ga
  14,17,jisay woh zabardasti halaq se utaarnay ki koshish kere ga aur mushkil hi se utaar sakay ga mout har taraf se is par chhai rahay gi magar woh marnay nah paye ga aur agay aik sakht azaab is ki jaan ka laago rahay ga
  14,18,jin logon ne apne rab se kufar kya hai un ke aamaal ki misaal uss raakh ki si hai jisay aik tofani din ki aandhi ne ura diya ho woh apne kiye ka kuch bhi phal nah pa saken ge yahi parlay darjay ki gum gushtagihai
  14,19,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ne aasman o zameen ki takhleeq ko haq par qaim kya hai? woh chahay to tum logon ko le jaye aur aik nai khalqat tumhari jagah le aeye
  14,20,aisa karna is par kuch bhi dushwaar nahi hai
  14,21,"aur yeh log jab ikathay Allah ke samnay be naqaab hon ge to uss waqt inn mein se jo duniya mein kamzor thay o hay unn logon se jo barray banay hue thay, kahin ge"" duniya mein hum tumahray tabay thay, ab kya tum Allah ke azaab se hum ko bachanay ke liye bhi kuch kar saktay ho ?"" woh jawab den ge"" agar Allah ne hamein nijaat ki koi raah dikhayi hoti to hum zaroor tumhe bhi dikha dete ab to yaksaa hai, khuwa hum jaz'fiz'(rona dhona ) karenya sabr, bahar-haal hamaray bachney ki koi soorat nahi """
  14,22,"aur jab faisla chuka diya jaye ga to shetan kahe ga"" haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ne jo waday tum se kiye thay o hay sab sachey thay aur mein ne jitne waday kiye un mein se koi bhi poora nah kya mera tum par koi zor to tha nahi, mein ne iss ke siwa kuch nahi kya ke apne rastay ki taraf tumhe dawat di aur tum ne meri dawat par labbaik kaha ab mujhe malamat nah karo, apne aap hi ko malamat karo yahan nah mein tumhari faryaad rassi kar sakta hon aur nah tum Meer y is se pehlay jo tum ne mujhe khudai mein shareek bana rakha tha mein is se buri alzmh hon, aisay zaalmon ke liye dard naak saza yakeeni hai """
  14,23,"bakhilaf is ke jo log duniya mein imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain woh aisay baghoon mein daakhil kiye jayen ge jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi wahan woh apne rab ke azan se hamesha rahen ge, aur wahan un ka istaqbaal salamti ki mubarak baad se hoga"
  14,24,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ne kalma tayyiba ko kis cheez se misaal di hai? is ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik achi zaat ka darakht, jis ki jarr zameen mein gehri jami hui hai aur shaakhen aasman taq pohanchi hui hain"
  14,25,har aan woh apne rab ke hukum se apne phal day raha hai yeh misalein Allah is liye deta hai ke log inn se sabaq len
  14,26,"aur kalma khabisa ki misaal aik bad zaat darakht ki si hai jo zameen ki satah se ukhaar phenka jata hai, uss ke liye koi istehkaam nahi hai"
  14,27,"imaan laane walon ko Allah aik qoul saabit ki bunyaad par duniya aur akhirat, dono mein Sabaat ataa karta hai, aur zaalmon ko Allah bhatka deta hai Allah ko ikhtiyar hai jo chahay kere"
  14,28,tum ne dekha unn logon ko jinhon ne Allah ki Nemat payi aur ussay kufran Nemat se badal dala aur ( apne sath ) apni qoum ko bhi halakat ke ghar mein jhonk diya
  14,29,"yani jahannum, jis mein woh jhulsay jayen ge aur woh bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
  14,30,"aur Allah ke kuch humsar tajweez kar liye taakay woh inhen Allah ke rastay se bhatka den inn se kaho, acha mazay kar lau, aakhir kaar tumhe palat kar jana dozakh hi mein hai"
  14,31,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, mere jo bande imaan laaye hain unn se keh do ke namaz qaim karen aur jo kuch hum ne unn ko diya hai, uss mein se khulay aur chupay ( raah kher mein ) kharch karen qabal iss ke ke woh din aeye jis mein nah khareed o farokht hogi aur nah dost nawazi hosakay gi"
  14,32,"Allah wohi to hai jis ne zameen aur asmano ko peda kya aur aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ke zareya se tumhari rizaq rasani ke liye terhan terhan ke phal peda kiye jis ne kashti ko tumahray liye maskhar kya ke samandar mein uss ke hukum se chalay aur daryaaon ko tumahray liye maskhar kya"
  14,33,jis ne Sooraj aur chaand ko tumahray liye maskhar kya ke lagataar chalay ja rahay hain aur raat aur din ko tumahray liye maskhar kya
  14,34,jis ne woh sab kuch tumhe diya jo tum ne manga agar tum Allah ki nematon ka shumaar karna chaho to kar nahi satke haqeeqat yeh hai ke ensaan bara hi be insaaf aur nashukara hai
  14,35,"yaad karo woh waqt jab ibrahim ne dua ki thi ke"" parvar-digaar, iss shehar ko aman ka shehar bana aur mujhe aur meri aulaad ko buut parasti se bacha"
  14,36,"parvar-digaar, inn buton ne bahuton ko gumraahi mein dala hai ( mumkin hai ke meri aulaad ko bhi yeh gumraah kar den, lehaza unn mein se ) jo mere tareeqay par chalay woh mera hai aur jo mere khilaaf tareeqa ikhtiyar kere to yaqeenan to dar guzar karne wala meharban hai"
  14,37,"parvar-digaar, mein ne aik be aabb o giyah waadi mein apni aulaad ke aik hissay ko tairay mohtaram ghar ke paas laa basaayaa hai parvar-digaar, yeh mein ne is liye kya hai ke yeh log yahan namaz qaim karen, lehaza to logon ke dilon ko inn ka mushtaq bana aur inhen khanay ko phal day, shayad ke yeh shukar guzaar banin"
  14,38,"parvar-digaar, to jaanta hai jo kuch hum chupatay hain aur jo kuch zahir karte hain"" aur waqai Allah se kuch bhi chhupa howa nahi hai, nah zameen mein nah asmano mein"
  14,39,""" shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne mujhe iss burhapay mein Ismael aur ishaq jaisay betay diye, haqeeqat yeh hai ke mera rab zaroor dua santa hai"
  14,40,"a y mere parvar-digaar, mujhe namaz qaim karne wala bana aur meri aulaad se bhi ( aisay log utha jo yeh kaam karen ) parvar-digaar, meri dua qubool kar"
  14,41,"parvar-digaar, mujhe aur mere walidain ko aur sab imaan laane walon ko uss din maaf kar dejyu jabkay hisaab qaim hoga """
  14,42,"ab yeh zalim log jo kuch kar rahay hain, Allah ko tum is se ghaafil nah samjhoo Allah to aِnhin taall raha hai uss din ke liye jab haal yeh hoga ke ankhen phati ki phati reh gayi hain"
  14,43,"sir uthaye bhage chalay ja rahay hain, nazrain oopar jami hain aur dil uray jatay hain"
  14,44,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, uss din se tum aِnhin dra-o jabkay azaab aِnhin alay ga uss waqt yeh zalim kahin ge ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein thori si mohlat aur day day, hum teri dawat ko labbaik kahin ge aur Rasolo-n ki pairwi karen ge"" ( magar inhen saaf jawab day diya jaye ga ke ) kya tum wohi log nahi ho jo iss se pehlay kasmain kha kha kar kehte thay ke hum par to kabhi zawaal aana hi nahi hai ?"
  14,45,halaank tum un qomon ki bustiyon mein reh bas chuke thay jinhon ne apne oopar aap zulm kya tha aur dekh chuke thay ke hum ne unn se kya sulooq kya aur unn ki misalein day day kar hum tumhe samgha bhi chuke thay
  14,46,"unhon ne apni saari hi chaalein chal dekhen, magar unn ki har chaal ka toar Allah ke paas tha agarchay unn ki chaalein aisi ghazab ki theen ke pahar unn se tal jayen"
  14,47,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum hargiz yeh gumaan nah karo ke Allah kabhi apne Rasolo-n se kiye hue wadon ke khilaaf kere ga Allah zabardast hai aur intiqam lainay wala hai"
  14,48,dra-o inِhain uss din se jabkay zameen aur aasman badal kardrad kuch se kuch kar diye jayen ge aur sab ke sab Allah wahid Qahar ke samnay be-naqaab haazir ho jayen ge
  14,49,uss roz tum mujrimon ko dekho ge ke zanjeeroon mein haath paon jakray hunge
  14,50,tarkol ke libaas pehnay hue hon ge aur aag ke sholay unn ke cheharon par chaaye ja rahay hon ge
  14,51,yeh iss liye hoga ke Allah har mutnaqas ko is ke kiye ka badla day ga Allahko hisab letay kuch der nahi lagti
  14,52,"yeh aik pegham hai sab insanon ke liye, aur yeh bheja gaya hai is liye ke unn ko iss ke zareya se khabardaar kar diya jaye aur woh jaan len ke haqeeqat mein khuda bas aik hi hai aur jo aqal rakhtay hain woh hosh mein aa jayen"
